  <brief_title>PI and Tissue Perfusion for Different Approaches of Brachial Plexus Block</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Different Approaches of Infraclavicular Brachial Plexus Block on Perfusion Index and Tissue Perfusion: A Prospective Randomized Trial</official_title>
