  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To compare the two different approaches of infraclavicular brachial plexus block in forearm,&#xD;
      wrist and hand surgery in terms of perfusion index, tissue oxygenation, sensory and motor&#xD;
      block onset time and total effect time, first analgesic time, side effects and complications,&#xD;
      and duration of block application.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
